results.overview: Combat has taken its toll on Rambo, but he's finally begun to find inner peace in a monastery. When Rambo's friend and mentor Col. Trautman asks for his help on a top secret mission to Afghanistan, Rambo declines but must reconsider when Trautman is captured.
results.title: Rambo III

results.overview: Forced by his family to enlist in the army, Johnny Rambo goes to the squad of the "misfits". Very soon, because of his clumsiness, the group becomes a real nightmare for the drill sergeant, who is none other than Johnny's father. However, because of a casual incident, they become heroes in view of the commander, who entrusts them to a dangerous mission, within the terrotirio dominated by the enemy. There Johnny will meet a beautiful secret agent with whom he will live all kinds of crazy adventures. Filipino parody of the Rambo saga.
results.title: Johny Tan-Go Rambo Part III

results.overview: Forced by his family to join the army, Johnny Rambo ends up in the squad of misfits.
